# 🧠 CRITICAL INTERVIEW THEORY (MUST MASTER)

---

## 🔥 STREAM INTERNALS

* Does each operation create new loop?
  👉 ❌ No → **Loop fusion (single pass)**

* When does execution start?
  👉 Only at terminal operation

---

## 🔥 map vs flatMap

| map            | flatMap  |
| -------------- | -------- |
| 1 → 1 mapping  | 1 → many |
| returns nested | flattens |

---

## 🔥 reduce vs collect

| reduce             | collect                 |
| ------------------ | ----------------------- |
| immutable          | mutable                 |
| simple aggregation | complex transformations |

---

## 🔥 groupingBy

* Internally uses:

```java
Map<K, List<V>>
```

---

## 🔥 Parallel Streams

* No ordering guarantee
* Needs stateless operations
* Avoid side effects

